1.4
log
@everyting -> everything
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: ofwreal.S,v 1.3 2003/10/16 05:03:22 deraadt Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: ofwreal.S,v 1.1 1996/09/30 16:34:51 ws Exp $	*/

